race.comment: YABBY PUMP (1) handy gelding near his top third-up. Produced a good set of closing splits late when a narrow second over 1300m at Hawkesbury in fast time. Can race closer today with the claim and assert his class late. SHE SWINGS (9) relished the extra ground at her second run back when getting off the mark at start six for a comprehensive win over 1300m at Hawkesbury. Winning rider sticks and can play a leading role again. COYOTE (4) rewarded for his consistency at start three when surging late for a game maiden win over 1400m at Hawkesbury. Can get across from the sticky gate and run into the minor money. REBEL RHAPSODY (3) has been up for a long time this campaign and is racing in career-best form. Failed to give up with the 57.5kg when a courageous third over 1500m here. Winning rider hops back on and not to be overlooked.
